      <originalsloc id="aspace_3bcbf8e183c0d946ea90b638afe6027b">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection is available on microfilm (HM 250) and in the Ernst Jäckh Papers (MS 467).   The papers consist of correspondence, reports, and other material relating to political and diplomatic affairs in Turkey and the Middle East from 1908 to 1921, particularly in relation to interests of the German Foreign Office in that area. Papers of the naval attache Hans Humann form the bulk of the material.</p>  
